              Conversion-Optimized
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm lg:text-base">
              Every title and description is crafted to maximize appeal and
              drive sales using proven copywriting principles.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div
          class="group flex flex-col bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1"
